Mikel Conrad https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mikel_Conrad 0 Mikel Conrad (30 July 1919 – 11 September 1982) was an American actor and film director, writer and producer. He was born in Columbus, Ohio and died in Los Angeles, California at the age of 63. Mikel_Conrad ( 30_July_1919 – 11_September_1982 ) was an_American_actor_and_film_director , writer_and_producer .
